  "description": "<p>📦 <strong>Hiring: Full-Time Packer</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Yishun<br />🕙 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> 10:00am – 6:00pm<br />📅 <strong>Working Days:</strong> Monday to Friday, Alternate Saturdays<br /><br /><strong>Job Scope:</strong><br /><br />Picking and packing of goods<br />Labeling and sorting items<br />Assist in preparing orders for delivery<br />Keep work area clean and organized<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><p>Able to follow simple instructions<br />Physically fit and reliable<br />No experience required (training provided)<br /><br />Interested parties:<br />Click ''<strong>APPLY</strong>'' or<br />Send your resume to <em><strong>admin@psmanpower.com </strong></em>with the subject line: “<em><strong>NSFT3134 Application</strong></em>”</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br />By applying for this role, you consent to PS Manpower Pte Ltd PDPA<br />Data collected is strictly used for recruitment purposes only.</p></p>",
